Bongeka Gamede (amụrụ n'abalị iri abụọ na abụọ n'ọnwa Mee n'afọ 1999) bụ onye ọgba egwuregwu bọọlụ South Africa nke na-agbara Mahadum nke Western Cape (UWC) na ndị otu ụmụ nwanyị South Africa bọọlụ dị ka onye nnọchiteanya nchekwa goolu.

Obodo Gamede bụ Ixopo na KwaZulu-Natal. Onye bụbu onye South Africa n'ogo ndị dị afọ iri na asaa n'afọ iri abụọ, e tinyere ya na ndị otu South Africa maka 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup n'agbanyeghị na ọ nọchitebeghi anya ndị otu mba ahụ na ọkwa okenye na mbụ

Ọ bụ nwa akwụkwọ na-agụ gbasara njem nlegharị anya na Mahadum nke Western Cape, maka nke a ọ kwụsịrị ule afọ mbụ ya iji pụta na asọmpi ahụ. O gbara egwuregwu izizi ya na mba ụwa na egwuregwu enyi na enyi tupu iko mba ụwa megide Norway N'abalị abụọ nke ọnwa June 2019, na-mkpọba  dị ka onye nnọchi anya na mmeri ọkpụ asaa asatara abụọ nke South Africa.
Àtụ:South Africa squad 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup
